The endeavour of the author to find a dignified and classica] title for .the important official ‘quern constabularium dicimus: has led him into error. ‘Miles gregarius ' in its strict sense is a common soldier, one of the flock, not, as our author seems to have supposed, the chief soldier of the flock.
